    <p class="p2-text">{exchange.name} was founded in {exchange.founded} and is incorporated in {exchange.headquarters}. The exchange serves more than {exchange.users} registered users across a wide range of countries. {exchange.name} is known for its extensive altcoin selection and its accessible onboarding — standard spot trading does not require identity verification, making it one of the few major exchanges with a genuine no-KYC option.</p>
